ect="text" data-key="1875"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1875:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">注意，这条记录里没有一句“模型不够细心”，而是细致记录了：哪一个状态平面混了，哪个工具入口放宽了参数来源，哪道闸门发现了错误，以及下一次工具调用前应该出现什么提醒。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-bd47a0e9" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1876"><img class="se-423aa5c2" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/editor-compose/resourceimage/compose/de/dc/dedf7224bb7d37d129aec245bc1431dc.jpg"></div><div class="se-7c401e72  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1877"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1878"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1878:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">执行型失败优先使用结构化召回。相同任务族、相同工具、相同机械状态键，通常比纯文本相似更能指向同类事故。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-ec667fcd" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1879"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1880"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1880:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">把“记录、审查、召回”这条链跑通</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-8276b264  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1881"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1882"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1882:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">有了失败日记的 6 层结构，下面我们把“记录、审查、召回”这条链跑通。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-5e19b104  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1883"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1884"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1884:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">具体的召回点一般有三个。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-d1142c20" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1885"><div class="se-5e4ee632 se-cc3e8c67" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1886"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1887"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1887:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">新任务启动时，召回同 task_family 的高风险失败。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-2196f95c se-6bb33b63" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1888"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1889"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1889:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">任务规划时，召回同场景的经验教训。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-9209c61c se-5c98814c" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1890"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1891"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1891:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">高风险工具调用前，按工具名和机械参数召回。对执行型 Agent，工具调用前那一刻往往最有价值，因为真正的副作用就发生在那里，这时候召回一张短短的“危险卡”，好过在上下文里面塞十条长日志。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-041ea7cc  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1892"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1893"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1893:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">把这套召回放到下个月的流程。7 月结算一启动，又是跨租户写入薪资组的同类场景，新任务启动这个召回点先命中 task_family，规划时再命中场景，等 Agent 走到 </span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="1894" class="se-bf012e71"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1895"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1895:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">create_payroll_batch</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1896"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1896:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> 前那一刻，按工具名加 </span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="1897" class="se-bf012e71"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1898"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1898:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">payroll_group_id</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1899"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1899:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> 把这条经验顶到最前。Agent 还没动手，先读到一句“跨租户 id 写入前校验归属”。6 月这一跤，就这样变成了 7 月的拦截。一次任务的教训，被我们成功喂给了下一次任务。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-d5ed3ad0" data-code-language="python" data-slate-type="pre" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1900"><div class="se-b83998a0 se-f9de4cec"><span></span></div><div class="se-ac7563a2 se-6ef1a4f6"><span></span></div><div class="se-b48780ab"><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="1"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="2"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="3"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="4"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="5"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="6"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="7"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="8"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="9"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="10"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="11"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="12"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="13"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="14"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="15"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="16"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="17"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="18"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="19"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="20"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-line-number="21"></div><div class="se-312801db se-4ed19f8e" data-code-l