v><div class="simplebar-placeholder" style="width: auto; height: 1140px;"></div></div><div class="simplebar-track simplebar-horizontal" style="visibility: visible;"><div class="simplebar-scrollbar" style="width: 257px; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); display: block;"></div></div><div class="simplebar-track simplebar-vertical" style="visibility: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-scrollbar" style="height: 0px; display: none;"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="se-18c0e3b6  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2195"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2196"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2196:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这段代码的重点有两处。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-0b5be1b9" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2197"><div class="se-e1b510c0 se-e3fea95b" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2198"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2199"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2199:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">一是把 symptom、root_cause、repair、lesson、do_not 和召回条件分开存，系统才能检索、统计。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-37cf8986 se-a3a19467" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2200"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2201"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2201:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">二是只有审查通过的失败才能召回。</span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="2202" class="se-bf012e71"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2203"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2203:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Boundary</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2204"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2204:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> 先判断什么算失败，</span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="2205" class="se-bf012e71"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2206"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2206:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">EvidenceBundle</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2207"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2207:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> 把证据按之前进度追踪模式中我们讲的的三平面分开存，哪一步失败、当时以为在做什么、机械参数从哪来、原始观测在哪，失败才追得回去。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-ef404552  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2208"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2209"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2209:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">还要注意，召回不要只靠文本相似度。很多事故来自同一个业务动作、同一批机械参数、同一个工具入口，语义相似反而不是主线索。所以结构化召回键，也就是 task_family 加 tool 加 mechanical_keys，往往比纯 embedding 更可靠。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-c8a17912" data-slate-type="block-quote" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2210"><div class="se-36573411" data-slate-type="quote-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2211"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2212"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2212:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-a96bd026" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">咖哥发言：</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2213"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2213:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">除了在线召回之外，还可以进一步把失败轨迹重新标注和打包，转化成离线训练数据。不过，未经审查的失败直接拿去训练，可能把错误根因、过度概括的教训和错误边界一起内化进模型。因此，失败日记的第一目标，是让下一次任务少犯同类错误。训练则属于第二阶段。推荐的落地顺序是先跑通记录、审查、召回和注入。等失败日记里积累了足够多经过确认的高质量条目，再评估是否把它们变成训练数据。</span></span></span></div></div><h2 class="se-556d6076" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2214"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2215"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2215:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">失败日记本身也是攻击面</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-4e5c0d99  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2216"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2217"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2217:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">失败日记是一个长期记忆库，长期记忆库就是攻击面。未来的 Agent 攻击不只是提示词注入，还会有记忆注入、记忆投毒、记忆篡改。失败日记正好是这类攻击最理想的落点。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-09153082  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2218"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2219"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2219:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">如果有人往里写一条假教训，比如伪装成“跨租户写入这步可以跳过校验”，下次召回就被污染，Agent 反而会被这条假经验领着去犯错。向 Agent 的长期记忆里投毒，攻击成功率非常高，而正常任务几乎看不出异常，攻击者甚至不需要直接改记忆库，只靠普通对话就能诱导 Agent 自己把恶意记录写进去。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-a4f7b07e" data-slate-type="block-quote" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2220"><div class="se-36573411" data-slate-type="quote-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2221"><a data-slate-type="link" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="2222" class="se-6716688e se-bbfd0135"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2223"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2223:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">MemoryGraft</span></span></span></a><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2224"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2224:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> 把恶意流程伪装成“合法的、已验证过的最佳实践”，藏在普通文档里被 Agent 摄入，下次遇到相似任务，Agent 无需任何显式触发，就会检索、信任、照搬。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-bab33f85  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2225"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2226"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2226:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">为什么这么危险？因为记忆投毒和一次性提示词注入很不一样，它是持久的。恶意内容一旦写进记忆库，会在会话重启、上下文重置之后继续存活，几周后被一个语义相似的任务悄悄触发。因此，OWASP 的 Agentic 安全倡议把记忆投毒列为十五类威胁里的头号关注点。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-eb6d39c2  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2227"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2228"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2228:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">对失败日记的设计来说，这意味着两端都要治理。写入端要带来源，做来源标记、人审和会话隔离，一条失败日记从哪来、谁审过、属于哪个租户，都要可查，不能让任意输入直接写进可召回库。召回回来的历史经验，是“边界提醒”，不是“绝对真值（ground truth）”。Agent 看到一条历史教训，应该把它当成</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2229"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2229:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-4fc29de9" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">一个需要再核对的提示</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2230"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2230:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，而不是一条不容置疑的指令。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-6f274a46  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2231"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2232"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2232:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">最后，我们用下面的图给出失败日记的整体使用流程和生命周期。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-1f390b75" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2233"><img class="se-bd477293" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/editor-compose/resourceimage/compose/4f/bb/4fb174bd32856fe232e19ce260c334bb.jpg"></div><div class="se-5cdd5da6  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2234"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2235"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2235:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-63f3ae2f" data-slate-type="italic" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">写入端用来源追踪、租户隔离和审批防止记忆投毒；召回端把历史经验当作边界提醒，并与当前事实重新核验</span></span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-43438d27" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2236"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2237"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2237:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">失败日志的衡量指标</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-52b12289  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2238"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2239"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2239:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">失败日记的价值，不看库里存了多少条记录，而看同类失败是否减少。最值得关注的是四个指标：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-f385d029" data-slate-type="pre" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2240"><div class="se-6f4f611c se-1998b94c"><span></span></div><div class="se-c8d18def se-a1fd6b8d"><span></span></div><div class="se-8622da83"><div class="se-0d2b249d se-a12f4a0e" data-code-line-number="1"></div><div class="se-0d2b249d se-a12f4a0e" data-code-line-number="2"></div><div class="se-0d2b249d se-a12f4a0e" data-code-line-number="3"></div><div class="se-0d2b249d se-a12f4a0e" data-code-line-number="4"></div><div class="se-0d2b249d se-a12f4a0e" data-code-line-number="5"></div><div class="se-0d2b249d se-a12f4a0e" data-code-line-number="6"></div><div class="se-0d2b249d se-a12f4a0e" data-code-line-number="7"></div><div class="se-0d2b249d se-a12f4a0e" data-code-line-number="8"></div><div class="se-0d2b249d se-a12f4a0e" data-code-line-number="9"></div><div class="se-0d2b249d se-a12f4a0e" data-code-line-number="10"></div><div class="se-0d2b249d se-a12f4a0e" data-code-line-number="11"></div></div><div class="se-6e282940"><div data-simplebar="init"><div class="simplebar-wrapper" style="margin: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-observer-wrapper"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-observer"></div></div><div class="simplebar-mask"><div class="simplebar-offset" style="right: 0px; bottom: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-content-wrapper" style="height: auto; overflow: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-content" style="padding: 0px;"><div data-origin="pm_code_preview"><div class="se-522ce395 se-2cb603bc" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2241"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2242"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2242:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">重复失败率</span></span></span></div><div class="se-522ce395 se-2cb603bc" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2243"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2244"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2244:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">过去已记录的失败模式，又发生了多少次。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-522ce395 se-2cb603bc" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2245"></div><div class="se-522ce395 se-2cb603bc" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2246"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2247"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2247:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">召回有效率</span></span></span></div><div class="se-522ce395 se-2cb603bc" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2248"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2249"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2249:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">召回的经验中，有多少真正改变了计划或工具参数。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-522ce395 se-2cb603bc" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2250"></div><div class="se-522ce395 se-2cb603bc" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2251"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2252"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2252:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">漏召回率</span></span></span></div><div class="se-522ce395 se-2cb603bc" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2253"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2254"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2254:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">发生重复失败时，对应日记是否存在，却没有被召回。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-522ce395 se-2cb603bc" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2255"></div><div class="se-522ce395 se-2cb603bc" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2256"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2257"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2257:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">误提醒率</span></span></span></div><div class="se-522ce395 se-2cb603bc" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2258"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2259"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2259:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">召回了多少与当前任务无关的失败经验。</span></span></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="simplebar-placeholder" style="width: auto; height: 220px;"></div></div><div class="simplebar-track simplebar-horizontal" style="visibility: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-scrollbar" style="width: 0px; display: none;"></div></div><div class="simplebar-track simplebar-vertical" style="visibility: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-scrollbar" style="height: 0px; display: none;"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="se-3a9a047d  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2260"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2261"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2261:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">最核心的指标仍然是重复失败率。如果 </span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="2262" class="se-bf012e71"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2263"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2263:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">mechanical_state_mismatch</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2264"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2264:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> 一个月从十二次下降到三次，这套系统在积累经验。如果日记越写越多，但同类错误数量丝毫不降，问题通常出在召回点、分类、根因或教训写法上。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-ea1d412f" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2265"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2266"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2266:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">总结一下</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-0be80889  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2267"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2268"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2268:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">一架飞机发生事故，调查的目的不是只修好这一架飞机，也不是简单责怪某个飞行员。真正的目标，是读出黑匣子，把事故拆成可以命名、复现和改进的失败模式，再把改进传播到整支机队。失败日记就是 Agent 机队的黑匣子。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-018c4ab5  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2269"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2270"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2270:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">错误日志服务一次维修。黑匣子服务下一次飞行。失败日记要做的，就是把一个 Agent 的一次摔倒，变成所有同类任务以后都能绕开的坑。一个串租户事故，在失败日记中可不再只是一条失败记录，而成为每一次跨租户薪酬写入之前都会出现的护栏。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-41f445e7" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2271"><div class="se-cd140723 se-cd25ae0b" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2272"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2273"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2273:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">记失败日记的时候，要分清失败边界、失败分类、证据包、根因补救、召回触发器和留存审查。不要把失败写成一段故事，更不要用“模型太粗心”这种无法行动的根因。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-b9091aa7 se-81f73fe5" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2274"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2275"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2275:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">用失败日记的时候，要在下一次同类任务的关键入口主动召回，尤其是高风险工具调用前。结构化任务族、工具名和机械状态键，通常比纯语义相似更可靠。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-e98dd5db se-3a0cf138" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2276"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2277"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2277:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">管失败日记的时候，要有审批状态、分档留存和来源追踪。只有经过确认的失败经验才能进入召回；召回到的经验也只能作为风险提醒，不能替代当前事实和规则。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-a07517bd  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2278"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2279"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2279:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">那么，从哪里开始落地呢？可以先挑一条高重复、高损失的任务族，例如薪资结算、报销审批、合同审阅或生产发布。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-c39ef447" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2280"><div class="se-76fb1505 se-1c415523" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2281"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2282"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2282:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第一步，把上一讲 Verification Gate 产生的 </span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="2283" class="se-bf012e71"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2284"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2284:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">gate_failure</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2285"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2285:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> 和 </span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="2286" class="se-bf012e71"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2287"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2287:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">safety_failure</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2288"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2288:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> 自动转成失败日记草稿。这里的证据最完整，最容易起步。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-aee67ce3 se-7df01513" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2289"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2290"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2290:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第二步，设计八到十二个失败类别，以及 </span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="2291" class="se-bf012e71"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2292"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2292:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">draft—needs_review—approved—archived</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2293"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2293:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> 的审查状态机。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-22393843 se-9f775ce8" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2294"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2295"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2295:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第三步，只加几个召回入口：任务规划时和高风险工具调用前。先把短危险卡送到真正会发生副作用的位置。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-57fb33b9  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2296"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2297"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2297:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">最后盯住重复失败率，形成可运行的经验闭环。期待你在留言区分享你的思考，也推荐你把今天内容分享给有需要的朋友。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-ba54b390" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2298"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2299"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2299:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">思考题</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-369a30ed  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2300"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2301"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2301:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第一，最近一次 Agent 重复犯错是什么？它是没有被记录，还是记录了却没有在下一次任务里自动召回？</span></span></span></div><div class="se-52fc3177  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2302"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2303"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2303:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第二，挑一条失败记录看一看。它的根因是“模型幻觉、用户没说清”这种甩锅式解释，还是已经落到了具体的状态平面、工具入口和系统改进动作？</span></span></span></div><div class="se-eef1d401  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2304"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2305"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2305:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第三，你的失败经验在什么时刻出现？任务开始、任务规划，还是高风险工具调用前？它出现的位置，真的来得及改变行动吗？</span></span></span></div><div class="se-b20ec43e  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2306"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2307"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2307:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第四，如果有人向失败日记里写入一条伪装成最佳实践的恶意经验，你的来源追踪、审查机制和租户隔离能不能挡住？</span></span></span></div><div class="se-3f50cb34  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2308"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2309"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2309:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">期待你在留言区踊跃发言，也推荐你把今天的内容分享给吐槽过“Agent 总是同一个问题翻车”的朋友。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-6f8249e5" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2310"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2311"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2311:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">模块小结</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-f1fc9c85  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2312"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2313"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2313:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">到这里，记忆模式组的四个模式就讲完了。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-ee34d12f" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2314"><div class="se-aea006f3 se-c4972770" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2315"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2316"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2316:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">分层保留解决“架”，给记忆建货架。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-8e00eb36 se-245a2323" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2317"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2318"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2318:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">RAG 解决“取”，从外部大库里取回证据。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-fb95fbfb se-24074116" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2319"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2320"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2320:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">进度追踪解决“录”，把长任务记成能对账、能续跑的账。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-9e917528 se-f0fa1e9c" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2321"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2322"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2322:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">失败日记解决“省”，把一次摔跤变成下一次任务的护栏。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-fcb0ed00  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2323"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2324"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2324:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">一次任务，从搭货架、取证据、记进度，到记教训，走完了记忆的完整生命周期。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-6a58320b  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2325"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2326"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2326:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">程序性记忆，也就是把成功流程固化成可复用技能包，我们留到后面的反思模式组继续展开。下一讲开始，我们进入推理模式组。记忆解决的是过去的经验怎样留下来；推理要解决的是，当感知到的信息和召回的经验都摆在工作台上以后，Agent 怎样把它们组织成可靠判断和可执行计划。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-9639b003" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2327"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2328"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2328:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">参考资料</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-49d179ea" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2329"><div class="se-07d0a9ff" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2330"><div class="se-e53213ab se-a42537bb" data-code-line-number="1"></div><div class="se-c8db8fb9"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2331"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2331:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Shinn et al. </span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2332"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2332:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-63f3ae2f" data-slate-type="italic" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">Reflexion: Language Agents with Verbal Reinforcement Learning</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2333"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2333:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">. NeurIPS 2023, arXiv:2303.11366.</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-e3553fbf" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2334"><div class="se-d449473e se-3f4d51ae" data-code-line-number="2"></div><div class="se-071fb497"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2335"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="2335:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Toyota Production System / Five Whys（丰田佐吉 1930s，大野耐一纳入 TPS）.</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-023c7dcf" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2336"><div class="se-b1ecc928 se-3eedd1e7" data-code-line-number="3"></div><div class="se-a80ca587"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="2337">